author: CNN
description: Beyond her vibrant wardrobe and signature bowl cut, Atsuko Okatsuka is known for turning family trauma into laughs. The comedian recalls her grandmother bringing her to the US under the guise of a vacation and jokes about an "Atsuko planet" where everyone shares her haircut. CNN’s Hanako Montgomery caught up with Okatsuka in Tokyo and shared a playful moment of copying her signature look.
title: Atsuko Okatsuka on her signature bowl cut and finding home in comedy

author: CNN
description:
From South Korea, Japan, and Pakistan, three celebrated talents open up about the journeys that shaped them and the futures they’re building. Hyun Bin reflects on two decades as one of the Korean Wave’s most recognizable leading men. Comedian and writer Atsuko Okatsuka shares how humor, heritage, and her signature bowl cut helped her find belonging. And, actress Mahira Khan looks back on her path from hustling in California to becoming Pakistan’s beloved superstar and a UNHCR Goodwill Ambassador. 

CNN’s Kristie Lu Stout, Will Ripley and Hanako Montgomery sit down with each of them across Hong Kong, Tokyo, and beyond for candid conversations about growth, identity, and the year ahead. 

0:00 Hyun Bin
3:05 Atsuko Okatsuka
7:15 Mahira Khan

#HyunBin #AtsukoOkatsuka #MahiraKhan
title: Hyun Bin, Atsuko Okatsuka and Mahira Khan on what's next in 2026

author: CNN
description: Denmark’s national postal service, PostNord, has delivered its final letter, marking the end of a 400-year tradition as digital communication replaces physical mail. The move makes Denmark the first country to conclude that letter delivery is no longer essential—or economically viable—in the digital age.
title: Denmark’s postal service ends letter delivery after 400 years

author: CNN
description: From blockbuster films to a groundbreaking, though delayed Netflix debut, "Pakistan’s Sweetheart" Mahira Khan calls 2025 a “wholesome surprise.” But beyond the spotlight, Khan embraces her role as a UNHCR Goodwill Ambassador, championing Afghan refugees, women’s rights, and mental health awareness. In conversation with CNN’s Kristie Lu Stout, Khan reflects on her humbling journey from California hustle to global stardom and how she hopes to carry forward with lessons learned into 2026.
title: Pakistan superstar Mahira Khan learned to hustle at a Brookstone in LA

description: Hyun Bin is one of South Korea’s leading men. He shot to global fame with the Netflix hit Crash Landing on You, where he played a stoic North Korean officer. description:
The Texas firm Ocean Infinity is starting its third attempt to find the Boeing 777 that disappeared in March 2014 while operating Malaysia Airlines Flight 370 from Kuala Lumpur to Beijing. The firm has signed a "no-find, no fee" contract with the Malaysian government and is using underwater robots to scan the ocean floor.
0:00 CNN's Wolf Blitzer speaks with CNN aviation safety analyst and author of "Malaysia Airlines Flight 370" David Soucie about the search's prospects
4:42 Wolf Blitzer speaks with oceanographer David Gallo about underwater searches
#MH370 #MalaysiaAirlinesFlight370 #News
title: New search for Malaysia Airlines Flight 370 underway
